"During vendor record creation, where is the vendor name sourced from for an individual with Singpass?","The vendor name for an individual with Singpass is sourced from the government database, Enterprise Data Hub (EDH). Specifically, the vendor name is auto-populated from the official name registered in the government EDH and is not editable. [Source: Create_Update_Vendor_Record.pdf, Page 8]","[{'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=720x540 at 0x22158F33110>, 'source': 'Document Create_Update_Vendor_Record.pdf, page 8'}, {'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=720x540 at 0x21FED3A9820>, 'source': 'Document Create_Update_Vendor_Record.pdf, page 22'}, {'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=720x540 at 0x22026936FC0>, 'source': 'Document LoginRegister.pdf, page 5'}, {'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=720x540 at 0x21FEC5F6300>, 'source': 'Document LoginRegister.pdf, page 18'}, {'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=720x540 at 0x2202A294C80>, 'source': 'Document LoginRegister.pdf, page 27'}]"
