What are the system maintenance windows during which vendor details cannot be updated?,"- The vendor details cannot be updated during the Telegraphic Transfer (TT) maintenance window. Specifically, updates are not possible when the TT bank details function is being maintained; in this document, it is indicated as the “Telegraphic Transfer (TT) option selected” maintenance period on the right-hand note. [Source: Document Create_Update_Vendor_Record.pdf, Page 17]","[{'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=720x540 at 0x21FB7DAFCB0>, 'source': 'Document Create_Update_Vendor_Record.pdf, page 17'}, {'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=720x540 at 0x21FE9FFD490>, 'source': 'Document Create_Update_Vendor_Record.pdf, page 37'}, {'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=595x842 at 0x21FEF67F950>, 'source': 'Document government-personal-data-protection-policies-jul21.pdf, page 27'}, {'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=595x842 at 0x21F9A87EDB0>, 'source': 'Document supplier_guide_detailed.pdf, page 24'}, {'image': <PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=595x842 at 0x220352A4FB0>, 'source': 'Document WHO World health statistics 2025.pdf, page 8'}]"
